title: 10/29/20 HOUR 1- Sean Salisbury
itunes:title: 10/29/20 HOUR 1- Sean Salisbury
description:
Sean Salisbury talks to Dan about trading JJ Watt. Sean tells Dan that you have to get rid of your loyalty and forget all about what he does in the community. Sean says the Texans don't have very many commodities left to trade.
